      "isPinned": false,
      "content": "Next revision of the wafer holder/ tape stretcher. \nI've thought a bit about the up vs. down stretch. \n\nThey each have their own quirks\nI will call this one **up**(the second image in your set), there is not a lot of room around the pusher part and homing the machine is potentially problematic. \n\nPushing **down** I can't quite figure a good way to \na) load a frame\nb) have the desired strength without becomming too bulky\n\nAlso both have issues with fitting motion components around, but I think those can be dealt with",
